{"tid":390493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【5級颶風】大西洋10年來最強颶風 「艾爾瑪」風眼得人驚","createTime":"2017-09-07T06:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T07:32:46.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4b1b1f14a6305f18bcdebf649d97f11e539f832","tid":390493,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"美國國家颶風中心表示，颶風艾爾瑪（Irma）已增強為「極度危險」的5級颶風，並於周三凌晨登陸加勒比海東北部島嶼，最終可能吹襲美國。<br />\n<br />\n從美國國家海洋和大氣管理局（NOAA）衞星拍到的片段見到，「艾爾瑪」風眼如漩渦般旋轉，令這被形容為大西洋10年來最強的颶風顯得更為可怕。<br />\n<br />\n5級颶風「艾爾瑪」最高持續風速達每小時295公里，預計登陸加勒比海法屬諸島後，接著朝海地及美國佛羅里達州前進，登陸時料將帶來100至200毫米雨量。<br />\n<br />\n國家颶風中心警告，這些雨量恐導致具威脅性命的暴洪與山泥傾瀉，「艾爾瑪」料也將引發「威脅生命的大浪與離岸流」，警告颶風警戒地區應盡速做好防災準備。「艾爾瑪」的警戒範圍從法屬西印度群島（French West Indies）到佛州，當中包括背風群島、英屬和美屬處女島、波多黎各等。<br />\n<br />\n「艾爾瑪」周末可能吹襲佛羅里達州，州長斯科特動員100名國民警衞在全州各地戒備，7,000名國民警衞周五會報到當值。該州南部外海佛羅里達礁島群的官員，正準備疏散遊客和居民。南部門羅縣表示周三日出後會開始強制疏散遊客，並正籌備疏散居民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170906/57174275\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170906%2F57174275&d=9KuE1y%2Fp8HLmKs9zaf6rKmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=4f6b486f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170906%2F57174275&h=3fd32041\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170906/57174275</a>"},{"pid":"a53f010a091b500b3257aeac3cba63fe372b4229","tid":390493,"uid":13025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:31:23.000Z","msg":"仲以為有飛機上影風眼圖"},{"pid":"c8052700c190dc8f011afc3f0ebb6ebb5b62be1d","tid":390493,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:31:40.000Z","msg":"【5級颶風】咁樣防風︰將膠椅沉入泳池 波多黎各或停電長達半年 <br />\n<br />\n 颶風 「艾爾瑪」（Irma）來勢洶洶，民眾把握時間做好防風措施，又買水囤糧，超市貨架被人一掃而空。<br />\n<br />\n住在格爾夫波特（Gulfport）的56歲居民克魯特（Jackie Kreuter）周三將室外遮陽傘收好，再將池邊家具如椅子等拋入池水中，認為這樣可以防止它們被大風吹走，又為房子加裝防風板。她們一家人包括她的丈夫、女兒、媽媽、姊妹、孫子、5隻狗及一隻鳥之後會前往奧卡拉（Ocala）避風。<br />\n<br />\n至周一中午，佛州南部不少雜貨店已被人掃光食水，周二早上才再有貨，多間建築材料行亦人頭湧湧，民眾購買大批木板加固窗門防風。波多黎各和美屬處女島已進入緊急狀態，超市及油站外大排長龍。<br />\n<br />\n波多黎各居民更已做好長期停電的打算，電力公司預計颶風造成的破壞，可能令部份地區停電長達4至6個月，「但部份地區可能在一星期內恢復供電」。當地電力設施因經濟衰退而失修，波多黎各居民去年也曾經歷大停電。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170906/57174847\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170906%2F57174847&d=9KuE1y%2Fp8HLmKs9zaf6rKmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=75c65ee0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170906%2F57174847&h=73e1b17c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170906/57174847</a>"},{"pid":"6bfe1e1d17b4562702af849067907a6e8a7941bf","tid":390493,"uid":13678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:32:20.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e2d89e811c86f79cd897493074f2189fc4ce941b","tid":390493,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲以為有飛機上影風眼圖</blockquote><br />\n【5級颶風】勇！「風暴獵人」飛越風眼 畫面驚心動魄 <br />\n<br />\n 被形容為大西洋10年來最強颶風「艾爾瑪」（Irma），預料趨向美國佛羅里達州。美國國家海洋及大氣管理局（NOAA）有英勇的「風暴獵人」，駕駛偵察機穿越「艾爾瑪」的風眼，近距拍攝它的情況，讓當局得到寶貴的資料分析「艾爾瑪」的路徑及強度等。<br />\n<br />\nNOAA的一班「風暴獵人」自過去周末開始，已多次飛越「艾爾瑪」收集有用資料，團隊周二發佈的影片驚心動魄。影片可見他們駕駛螺旋偵察機飛進「艾爾瑪」的風眼牆（eyewall），狂風及暴雨吹打著機身，突然間機外變得相對風平浪靜，因為偵察機已進入了「艾爾瑪」的風眼。<br />\n<br />\n今次穿越「艾爾瑪」的是改良版的P-3獵戶座（Orion）偵察機「WP-3D Orion」，機師在飛近風暴後釋放載有GPS的探測儀，用來搜集風向、風速、濕度等資料，讓專家分析出風暴的結構及強度；機上亦裝設了特別的雷達系統如「多普勒雷達」（Doppler radar）等，全方位掃描風暴形態。<br />\n<br />\nNOAA表示偵察機本周仍會多次飛近「艾爾瑪」，以取得更多資料分析風暴詳情。美國共有兩隊官方「風暴獵人」，除了NOAA屬下的一隊，還有隸屬美國空軍的一隊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170906/57176287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170906%2F57176287&d=9KuE1y%2Fp8HLmKs9zaf6rKmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=89e87349\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170906%2F57176287&h=80156e32\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170906/57176287</a>"},{"pid":"699149db46e1dfdf2aef2e7ca112789fb3373ac9","tid":390493,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c33884d2ed94c198f6b6b7ea8147c5b52467a7","tid":390493,"uid":47663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"準備登機，uncle 全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4995c8966be7bd6863540a8296d3c00123d370","tid":390493,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c1ab47c5498ae63b5e6e33e2470589c76f6d06a","tid":390493,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>準備登機，uncle 全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知全盛時期一班機有幾多uncle 呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f9a02280bb9b7c53243abd22294e5555c68541","tid":390493,"uid":26544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/150018_3c0b4693bb4701d89a89eb345da7df06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F150018_3c0b4693bb4701d89a89eb345da7df06.jpg&h=0a149bdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cbc0d2d873006ebb33e4cafd6c232b3a582b403","tid":390493,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:01:50.000Z","msg":"自以為高高在上既lindanjai食晒花生 睇死幾時到香港吹到一棟都冇家破人亡 我就著草北行睇電視偷笑"},{"pid":"659678443fd6896e628a369051059cc534262f3e","tid":390493,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:03:52.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2b5bf010478ec52098377a815dec9bb82bc6595c","tid":390493,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T07:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/150018_3c0b4693bb4701d89a89eb345da7df06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F150018_3c0b4693bb4701d89a89eb345da7df06.jpg&h=0a149bdf&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}